text: San Juan Bautista Tuxtepec (Nahuatl: "on the hill of rabbits") is a city in Oaxaca, Mexico. It is part of the Tuxtepec District of the Papaloapan Region. == References == Category:Cities in Mexico Category:Settlements in Oaxaca Category:14th-century establishments in Mexico
title: San Juan Bautista Tuxtepec
